longBusinessSummary: Juki Corporation manufactures and sells industrial sewing machines, industrial equipment, and household sewing machines in Japan and internationally. It offers industrial sewing machines for sewing apparel products, sportswear, shoes, bags, and car seats; household sewing machines, including professional, lock, and quilt sewing machines; and mounting related equipment to make electronic circuit boards. The company also provides sleep buster, a device to reduce traffic accidents and prevent overwork driving; and data entry systems. In addition, it is involved in the contract development, manufacturing, and processing business. Juki Corporation was founded in 1938 and is headquartered in Tama, Japan.
